The paper deals with 3D pose estimation from monocular images using Deep Learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a new Deep Learning architecture for structured prediction, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses joint dependencies, which is a topic in graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
